text:
骚穴水又滑又多，却太过紧致，硕大的阴茎就像闯入的怪物，甬道蠕动着想要将他赶出去，却层层迭迭吸吮着，让男孩的眼底发红，舒服的叹慰。
“嗯……好大……嗯啊……哥哥好棒……”她色色的舔舌，感觉到龟头触及到了那一层薄薄的膜，她注视着南安的眼睛，尾音仿佛带着钩子，骚的人心痒痒的：“想不想……干我……”
怎么可能不想！ 他都快要疯了！
“你，你知道段尽辞的下场吗？”
trans:
Her vaginal fluid was so slippery and abundant, but her vagina was too tight. The huge penis was like a monster intruding, and the passage was squirming as if trying to push it out, but sucking it layer upon layer, making the boy’s eyes turn red and he sighed in comfort.
“Mmm... So big... Mmm... You are so awesome...” She licked her lips lewdly, feeling the tip of his penis touch her maidenhead. She investigated Nan An’s eyes, her voice trailing off with a hook-like tone, making him feel itchy with desire, saying “Do you want to... fuck me...”
How could he not want to! He was almost crazy!
“Do, do you know what happened to Duan Jincheng at last?”
